title: Psycroptic - Symbols of Failure (2006)
description:
When I first listened to this CD, I obviously wasn&#039;t paying attention, because second time around I was able to fully realize the talent of this Death Metal band.  While listening to this, there were several occasions where I cocked my head sideways and said to myself "Damn, that was pretty damn good."  I believe that you shall do the same.  If you like it, go see them at Summer Slaughter this year.
